title: Ep. - 224 - MARGARET JOSEPHS FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW JERSEY  ASHLEY IACONETTI HAIBON
description:
Margaret Josephs from Real Housewives of New Jersey gives a mid-season window into the pony tail debacle, her friendship with Dolores and Teresa, and what really happened behind the scenes with Danielle and Marty. 

 

Ashley Iaconetti Haibon from The Bachelor reviews Back Street Boys: Show Em What You Are Made Of, a documentary film about the career of the vocal group Backstreet Boys.
